sequenceDiagram
    participant Operator as trustyai-service-operator
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant JobPod as lmes-job Pod<br/>(Batch Job)
    participant EvalHub as EvalHub Service<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant HFHub as HuggingFace Hub<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Model as Model Inference Endpoint<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant OCI as OCI Registry<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant MLflow as MLflow Server<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+

    Note over Operator,K8sAPI: Flow 1: EvalHub Job Execution

    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create Job + ConfigMap<br/>from LMEvalJob CR<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>JobPod: Schedule Pod<br/>Mount ConfigMap at /meta/job.json

    rect rgb(220, 240, 220)
        Note over JobPod: Phase: INITIALIZING
        JobPod->>JobPod: Load JobSpec from /meta/job.json<br/>(model, benchmark_id, params)
        JobPod->>EvalHub: POST status: INITIALIZING<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    end

    rect rgb(220, 230, 250)
        Note over JobPod: Phase: LOADING_DATA
        JobPod->>EvalHub: POST status: LOADING_DATA<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
        JobPod->>HFHub: GET datasets, tokenizers<br/>Auth: HF_TOKEN (optional)
        HFHub-->>JobPod: Dataset artifacts
    end

    rect rgb(255, 240, 220)
        Note over JobPod: Phase: RUNNING_EVALUATION
        JobPod->>EvalHub: POST status: RUNNING_EVALUATION<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
        loop For each evaluation batch (num_concurrent: 1-128)
            JobPod->>Model: POST /v1/completions<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (OPENAI_API_KEY)<br/>TLS 1.2+ (custom CA supported)
            Model-->>JobPod: Completion response
        end
        Note over JobPod: Compute metrics<br/>(117 metric functions)
    end

    rect rgb(240, 220, 240)
        Note over JobPod: Phase: POST_PROCESSING
        JobPod->>EvalHub: POST status: POST_PROCESSING<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    end

    rect rgb(220, 240, 235)
        Note over JobPod: Phase: PERSISTING_ARTIFACTS
        JobPod->>EvalHub: POST status: PERSISTING_ARTIFACTS<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
        JobPod->>OCI: Push result artifacts<br/>Auth: Registry Auth
        JobPod->>MLflow: Log metrics + run metadata<br/>Auth: Configurable
        MLflow-->>JobPod: run_id
    end

    rect rgb(220, 250, 220)
        Note over JobPod: Phase: COMPLETED
        JobPod->>EvalHub: POST results + status: COMPLETED<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    end

    Note over JobPod,Model: Flow 2: Offline/Disconnected Mode

    rect rgb(245, 245, 220)
        Note over JobPod: Offline Mode (HF_HUB_OFFLINE=1)
        participant S3 as S3/COS Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
        participant InitC as Init Container

        InitC->>S3: Download cached datasets<br/>Auth: AWS IAM / IBM COS
        S3-->>InitC: Dataset artifacts
        InitC->>InitC: Populate /test_data volume

        Note over JobPod: HF_HOME=/test_data<br/>HF_DATASETS_OFFLINE=1<br/>TRANSFORMERS_OFFLINE=1
        JobPod->>JobPod: Load data from /test_data (local)
        JobPod->>Model: POST /v1/completions<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
        Model-->>JobPod: Completion response
    end
